About PhotoCD
-------------

The  PhotoCD  loader is  an  ARexx-script  which  will load any PhotoCD-
picture into @{"ADPro" Link Requirements} assuming that you have either the @{"AsimPhoto" Link Requirements}
or the @{"Hpcdtoppm" Link Requirements} program.
@Endnode

@Node "Requirements" "PhotoCD.guide/Requirements"
@Next "Installation"
@Prev "About"
@Toc "Main"

Requirements
------------

An Amiga running OS 2.04+.

ASDG's Art Department Professional, Version 2.5.0+.

Asimware Innovation's AsimCDFS CD-ROM CONTROL SOFTWARE, Version 2.0+.
or
The Amiga version of hpcdtoppm, version 0.6+.

